Subject: Error during installation of pingcastle entreprise
Description:
Hello,

When trying to install pingcastle entreprise, i have an error message :

The installer has encountered an unexpected error installing this package. This may indicate a problem with this package. The error code is 26201.

Could you help me resolved this ?

Regards,
Thomas Bozzini
Solution_Comment__c: the issue was linked to a lack of rights form the user used to do the installation on the database engine. It is solved now.
